hopobject.body: Will I be paid weekly or monthly? lansoprazole 15 mg twice a day The programme he brings to Edinburgh reveals his distinctive taste: one new piece by Millepied himself, with music by one of LA Dance Project’s co-founders, Nico Muhly; a darkly difficult – and still controversial – piece by Merce Cunningham called Winterbranch; and William Forsythe’s quirkily thrilling Quintett. For future engagements Millepied is commissioning new work from such sought-after contemporary choreographers as Justin Peck and Emanuel Gat. ‘We’ve made extraordinary progress. People in Europe are programming us because they think the quality is high enough and that means that although we are small we might be first rate.’
